: "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rear view of young man walking towards detour\" data-id=\"1253985593\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8660px\" height=\"5773px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Leverage can be a powerful tool in increasing your returns, but it must be used very carefully. This brief guide will attempt to cover margin, hedging, and related issues.</p> <h2>Financing Your Investments</h2> <p>In theory, if your expected returns</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253985593/image_1253985593.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745551-how-to-use-leverage-to-boost-your-returns", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 16:24:25", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745550", "title": "TransUnion: A Perfect Stocking Stuffer For Your Portfolio This Christmas", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up of stack of credit cards\" data-id=\"88621207\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1153px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Adam Gault</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction </strong></h2> <p>TransUnion (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TRU\" title=\"TransUnion\">TRU</a></span>) is a U.S.-based consumer credit reporting <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/ix?doc=/Archives/edgar/data/1552033/000155203324000027/tru-20231231.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">agency</a> that specializes in providing risk and information solutions to both businesses and consumers. Founded over 50 years ago, the company has grown to maintain a vast database</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/88621207/image_88621207.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745550-transunion-a-perfect-stocking-stuffer-for-your-portfolio-this-christmas", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 16:16:48", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745547", "title": "Occidental Petroleum: Offsetting Near-Term Headwinds With Margin Optimization", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1631576538/image_1631576538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Occidental Chemical Corporation plant. Occidental Chemical manufactures chemicals including Sodium Silicate.\" data-id=\"1631576538\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1631576538/image_1631576538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1631576538/image_1631576538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1631576538/image_1631576538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1631576538/image_1631576538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1631576538/image_1631576538.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1631576538/image_1631576538.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1631576538/image_1631576538.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seeki